34 SECTION 1.16.(b) By April 1, 2026, the Department of Health and Human Services
35 shall consult with hospitals, prepaid health plans, and county departments of social services to
36 develop and distribute uniform guidance on the roles and responsibilities of each entity involved
37 in the delivery of case management services during a juvenile's stay in a hospital. This guidance
38 shall apply to any juvenile receiving protective services from a county department of social
39 services regardless of the juvenile's custody status. The guidance shall address, at a minimum,
40 the following:
