42 other contact with the juvenile while staying in the hospital.
43 (2) The nature, frequency, and type of communication among each entity
44 involved in providing services regarding ongoing treatment, referrals to
45 potential placements, and any additional information relevant to the juvenile's
46 services. There must be at least five days' notice of court hearings and
47 appearances related to the juvenile.
