26 "(e) Notwithstanding any time limitations contained in this section or the provisions of
27 G.S. 7B-324(a)(4), upon the filing of a petition for judicial review by an individual identified by
28 a director as a responsible individual, the district court of the county in which the abuse or neglect
29 report arose may review a director's determination of abuse or serious neglect at any time if less
