1 (3g)(3h) "FICA" means the taxes imposed by the Federal Insurance Contribution Act,
2 26 U.S.C. § 3101, et seq.
3 (3h)(3i) "Full-time employment" means employment which requires the employee to
4 work a regular schedule of hours per day and days per week established as the
